# Online Calculator

An attractive online calculator application with interactive buttons and sound effects. Created by Yugarakshini GunaSekar.

## Features

- Basic arithmetic operations (addition, subtraction, multiplication, division)
- Clear and backspace functionalities
- Interactive buttons with animations
- Click sound effect for button presses

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Setup

1. Clone the repository or download the code files.
2. Make sure you have the `click-sound.mp3` file in the same directory as your HTML file, or update the file path in the JavaScript code accordingly.
3. Open the `index.html` file in a web browser to use the calculator.

## Usage

- Enter numbers and operators using the calculator buttons.
- Click the "=" button to evaluate the expression.
- Use the "c" button to clear the display.
- Use the "<" button to delete the last character.
- Enjoy the interactive animations and sound effects!

